name: Homo Homini Lupus Est
description:
"Homo homini lupus est" --> L'homme est un loup pour l'homme --> Man is wolf to man! 


Being at the top of the food chain leads to cannibalism!

It was chosen to be Nooumena's "Controlled Freaks" album cover, my former progressive rock band. 

2017, watercolor and eau-forte etching, copper print, 60×60cm 

A limited edition of black and white traditional prints will be on sale soon, follow my twitter to be updated!

...and you can listen to the album here : Controlled Freaks--> https://nooumena.bandcamp.com/album/controlled-freaks
